      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S RAPTUROUS (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (29.96) at this track behind Canya Handle It in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can find winning form. CAWBOURNE ZARA (6) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 7 lengths at this track in a handy 29.81. Has a tricky draw to overcome but has the ability and in winning form. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Will go close again if runs up to latest. NATISA'S SECRET (3) was an effortless winner last time as she ran right away with a 10 length win at this track (30.04). Her last run is a proven strong form reference. Form should stack up. ASCEND FERN (1) was in the money last time at this track (29.74) in a NG, finishing a 5.5 lengths third. Has already won three times from this draw.",
